{"id": 2472, "genre": 1001, "title": "对话中你都遇过哪些“让人一愣”的尴尬提问？", "description": "丈二和尚，来分享一下那些让你摸不着头脑的被提问经历（图片来自：iStock © CSA-Archive）", "record_count": 3473, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180716171335DqLS9HymWhZEnoYv.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-20T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 292864, "content": "很久没联系的人问你“最近过得怎么样啊？”", "image": null, "praise_count": 263, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 293632, "content": "可以发答案给我吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408034}, {"id": 296704, "content": "考得不好时:你考了多少分\n考得好时:☞什么都不问", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425597}, {"id": 293633, "content": "老是被问今年多大了，有男朋友吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1394575}, {"id": 293889, "content": "我们现在干嘛呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410127}, {"id": 295681, "content": "很不熟的人对我说说“叫爸爸”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1420584}, {"id": 292866, "content": "认识没多久就问“你单身吗？”／初次约会“你有房有车吗？”", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 293634, "content": "不喜欢老是被问年龄，今年多大?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1394575}, {"id": 293890, "content": "你叫什么名字", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 59111}, {"id": 293635, "content": "面试，经理问我，你家种不种地……", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957294}, {"id": 293891, "content": "我喜欢你", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410146}, {"id": 292868, "content": "“你们知道为什么时空本源是量子纠缠吗？”和“我告诉你们......”的自问自答式提问", "image": null, "praise_count": 108, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 293636, "content": "生娃吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408057}, {"id": 293892, "content": "早上吃什么？\n中午吃什么？\n晚上吃什么？", "image": "img/option/option/2018072217400294g8mZFs0Dw2RUHV", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410157}, {"id": 293637, "content": "你的五年规划是什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671570}, {"id": 293638, "content": "丢了东西之后别人问：“丢哪了？”\n我要是知道丢哪了还会丢吗……", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1293978}, {"id": 293894, "content": "在不熟悉的亲戚面前，被迫叫称谓，，，，嗯？，，，你是？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410198}, {"id": 293639, "content": "叔叔，帮我拿....我TM明明是哥哥..", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408082}, {"id": 294151, "content": "你有和别人做过吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 355170}, {"id": 293640, "content": "我是东北人，南方有位老兄问我恨不恨日本人?", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1387786}, {"id": 293896, "content": "你们藏族人是不是很脏？?", "image": "img/option/option/20180722191144lPqQEch9mC3Duk1a", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410233}, {"id": 293641, "content": "考得咋样阿", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408086}, {"id": 293897, "content": "你一个人睡吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156655}, {"id": 293642, "content": "你的双眼皮贴飞出来了？or 你都是双眼皮了怎么还贴双眼皮贴？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 826252}, {"id": 293643, "content": "你觉得呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1179631}, {"id": 293899, "content": "你是好姑娘吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410260}, {"id": 295947, "content": "不熟的人，聊两句忽然就问，你家住哪？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1422015}, {"id": 293900, "content": "兄弟，你怎么胖了这么多?????", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410254}, {"id": 293645, "content": "朋友问我有多余的女朋友吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1159262}, {"id": 293646, "content": "你哪的？我都说了我东北滴，东北滴还有我说几遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408108}, {"id": 293647, "content": "你现在在哪里？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407223}, {"id": 294159, "content": "你是gay吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297298}, {"id": 296719, "content": "跟一堆大人在一起，她们聊天时突然问你一句“成绩怎么样呀？”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425414}, {"id": 293904, "content": "在吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1356723}, {"id": 294416, "content": "外地一朋友:“你们广东人是不是真的什么都吃？”???", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1413449}, {"id": 293649, "content": "你变得不像你了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408127}, {"id": 294161, "content": "大家都是成年人么，所以，放开聊，别害羞\n\n嗯嗯，是。\n\n那个，你今晚有空么？？\n\n额……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1411571}, {"id": 295185, "content": "你上几年级  \n我上高三  mmp", "image": "img/option/option/20180727171214BpP1ngFvsOMlZUIH", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1416537}, {"id": 293650, "content": "过的还好吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408124}, {"id": 293906, "content": "你是不是gay，没事儿我不歧视。女士你哪位？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482247}, {"id": 294162, "content": "说说你的五年计划和人生规划", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1411583}, {"id": 295442, "content": "你刚刚说什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417886}, {"id": 296466, "content": "你觉得我干的有什么结果。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424219}, {"id": 293651, "content": "你自己说怎么办", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408129}, {"id": 293907, "content": "你是怎么做到的！", "image": "img/option/option/20180722212814CS6PGb3lYj5rdnID.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1400462}, {"id": 293652, "content": "你为什么不请我…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137628}, {"id": 293653, "content": "这次考得怎么样", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1399031}, {"id": 293909, "content": "你怎么想的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410334}, {"id": 293654, "content": "so？？。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408151}, {"id": 293910, "content": "高考数学借我看一点←_←", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410377}]}